description: Tahir has challenged his friends to a game of pronunciation, and it's about to go down. They've each got five cards with five very difficult words on them. They try to pronounce each words and then try to guess what they mean. Maye is here to keep score and judge us harshly.

itunes.author: Tahir Moore
itunes.summary: Tahir has challenged his friends to a game of pronunciation, and it's about to go down. They've each got five cards with five very difficult words on them. They try to pronounce each words and then try to guess what they mean. Maye is here to keep score and judge us harshly.

title: Wording is Hard
